---
title: Vegan Tex-Mex Black Bean & Pepper Wrap with Rojo Rice, Pico de Gallo & Creamy Cilantro Sauce
description: Craving all the tantalizing flavors and textures of a burrito—minus the meat? Look no further. For this Tex-mex inspired vegan meal, you’ll layer the tortilla with fluffy tomato-scallion rice and Southwest-spiced green pepper-spiked black beans. Next up: fresh pico de gallo, a big drizzle of creamy dairy-free cilantro sauce (plus more for dipping), and a squeeze of lime. Fresh, healthy, and filling in 30 minutes–vamanos!
